{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0003", "text": "太隨意 情人換過六百萬次 不見我有哪次專注", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 0, 4, 0, 0, 2, 4, 2, 4, 2, 4, 3, 4, 5, 5, 5, 4, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["taai3", "ceoi4", "ji3", "cing4", "jan4", "wun6", "gwo3", "luk6", "baak3", "maan6", "ci3", "bat1", "gin3", "ngo5", "jau5", "naa5", "ci3", "zyun1", "zyu3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "隨意", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "情人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "換", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "六百萬", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "次", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不見", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哪次", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "專注", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0004", "text": "不專一 好像是 做壞事 做壞事 受盡萬衆不齒", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 9, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 4, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "zyun1", "jat1", "hou2", "zoeng6", "si6", "zou6", "waai6", "si6", "zou6", "waai6", "si6", "sau6", "zeon6", "maan6", "zung3", "bat1", "ci2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "專一", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好像", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "壞事", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "壞事", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "受盡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "萬衆", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不齒", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0005", "text": "很可惜 真相是 愛哪個 撇哪個 撇到何時爲止", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 9, 3, 3, 2, 4, 5, 4, 4, 5, 4, 4, 4, 0, 0, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["han2", "ho2", "sik1", "zan1", "si6", "oi3", "naa5", "go3", "pit3", "naa5", "go3", "pit3", "dou3", "ho4", "si4", "zi2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "很", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可惜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真相", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哪個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "撇", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哪個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "撇到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "何時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲止", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0006", "text": "我都不是太知 誰又覺得 變得心多 便有賞賜", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 3, 2, 4, 3, 0, 2, 4, 3, 4, 3, 3, 3, 2, 5, 9, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "dou1", "bat1", "si6", "taai3", "zi1", "seoi4", "jau6", "gok3", "dak1", "bin3", "dak1", "sam1", "do1", "bin6", "jau5", "soeng2", "ci3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "覺得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "變得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "賞賜", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0007", "text": "怎揀 若捕獲絕色的她 又幸會極品的她", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 9, 2, 2, 2, 2, 3, 3, 3, 2, 2, 2, 9, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zam2", "gaan2", "joek6", "bou6", "wok6", "zyut6", "sik1", "dik1", "taa1", "jau6", "hang6", "gik6", "ban2", "dik1", "taa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "怎揀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "捕獲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "絕色", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "她", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幸會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "極品", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "她", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0008", "text": "天真 無邪如蝴蝶穿花 爲何成人中之渣", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 3, 3, 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["tin1", "zan1", "mou4", "ce4", "jyu4", "wu4", "dip6", "cyun1", "faa1", "ho4", "sing4", "jan4", "zung1", "zi1", "zaa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "天真", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無邪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "蝴蝶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "穿花", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "成人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "中之渣", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0009", "text": "人人在指控謾罵 聲討我嗎", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 9, 4, 0, 2, 3, 9, 5, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jan4", "jan4", "zoi6", "zi2", "hung3", "maan4", "maa6", "sing1", "tou2", "ngo5", "maa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "人人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "指控", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "謾罵", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聲討", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0010", "text": "誰想過到 薄暮年華", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 4, 4, 2, 2, 0, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "soeng2", "gwo3", "dou3", "bok6", "mou6", "nin4", "waa4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "薄暮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "年華", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "人渣", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6209", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NjIwOQ_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
